data.description: Come see this beautiful new construction single story home. With 1280 sq/ft this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sits on just under a 1/4 acre. Home has Central Heat & Air, new appliances, and a dedicated laundry room with washer/dryer hook-ups.
